Enum XBeeTransmitStatus

    Serializable, Comparable<XBeeTransmitStatus>

    public enum XBeeTransmitStatus
extends Enum<XBeeTransmitStatus>
    Enumerates the different transmit status. Transmit status field is part of the TransmitStatusPacket indicating the status of the transmission.
    See Also:
    TransmitStatusPacket
